# EPOCH-VISION-GUARD

**Grok Vision Analyzer with Intelligent Vision → Text Fallback**  
A clean, robust, and production-oriented CLI tool for analyzing images using the xAI Grok API. It intelligently attempts all known Grok vision models first. If vision access is unavailable on your API key, it automatically falls back to text-only Grok models combined with enhanced PIL-generated image descriptions.
Designed for **AI research labs, red/blue/purple teams, security researchers, compliance teams, and enterprise users** who need reliable, auditable, and privacy-conscious image analysis — even under restricted API conditions.

