| 3. Structured Logging | Replace prints with `structlog` or `logging` to file + JSON | 8–10 hours | High | None |
| 4. Authentication & Secrets | Support secret managers (Vault, AWS SSM, etc.) | 10–12 hours | Medium | None |
| 5. Rate Limit & Quota Awareness | Dynamic backoff based on xAI headers | 6–8 hours | High | None |
| 6. Parallel Processing | Async batch processing with concurrency limit | 12–16 hours | Medium | None |
| 7. Web UI / API Wrapper | FastAPI endpoint + simple React/Vue dashboard | 3–5 days | Low | Optional |
| 8. Testing Suite | Unit + integration tests (pytest) | 8–12 hours | High | None |
| 9. Observability | Prometheus metrics + OpenTelemetry | 10–14 hours | Medium | None |
| 10. Full CI/CD Pipeline | GitHub Actions + security scanning | 6–8 hours | Medium | None |

**Total Estimated Time to Full Enterprise Grade:** **2–4 weeks** (solo developer) or **1–2 weeks** (small team).

