## Architecture

graph TD
    A[CLI Arguments + Interactive] --> B[EpochVisionGuard Class]
    B --> C[PIL Image Validation]
    C --> D[Vision Models Loop]
    D -->|Success| E[Analysis + PII Redaction]
    D -->|Fail| F[Text Fallback + Enhanced Description]
    F --> E
    E --> G[Retry + Backoff]
    G --> H[Session Metrics + Heartbeat]
    H --> I[JSON or Human Report]


Limitations
•	Requires a valid xAI API key
•	Text-fallback mode is descriptive only
•	PII redaction is best-effort (regex-based)
•	No built-in cloud storage or persistent database

Troubleshooting
Issue	Solution
"Model not found" errors	Tool automatically falls back
Rate limiting	Built-in retry + backoff
JSON output not working	Use --json flag
High latency	Reduce batch size or check API status
